{"tid":1861124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"{文宣不是萬能}醫護罷工要贏嘅唯一方法!!","createTime":"2020-02-04T04:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T04:41:22.000Z","uid":283912,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9d5d1b6e9aae5861f22043f378ead85b7b6bd2c9","tid":1861124,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:00:23.000Z","msg":"醫護罷工雖然得到主流民意支持<br />\n但對家已經發動鋪天蓋地底抹黑<br />\n~柒婆一如以往玩分化群眾鬥群眾<br />\n   一邊凶罷工醫護一邊捧留守嘅藍醫護<br />\n~HA高層喊哂口咁數病人點受影響<br />\n   瘋狂強調老人,嬰兒,癌症患者...道德勒索<br />\n~網上各大page五毛攻勢重新啟動<br />\n~岩岩肺炎死個件藍屍都想入埋醫護數<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個局照咁發展落去根本冇得贏:<br />\n社區爆發基本上已成定局<br />\n對家會出盡一切方法將責任推落醫護度<br />\n到時罷工目的達唔到,醫護要返岡位送頭<br />\n仲要揹埋對家夾硬屈落去嘅罪名<br />\n就算平安渡過呢關之後都被秋後算賬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n單靠文宣根本分擔唔到醫護承受嘅輿論壓力<br />\n但如果各行各業都加入罷工就唔同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時由<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>醫護vs政府</strong></span></span>變<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>全香港vs政府</strong></span></span><br />\n政府就不能夠將矛頭放哂係醫護度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地唔係一直等緊民怨大爆炸嘅機會發起真罷工咩?<br />\n今次罷工有哂理據有哂民意基礎有埋工會<br />\n工會手足們你地仲等咩?(尤其港鐵,巴士,航空業)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">馬上啟動全港大三罷!!</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支援醫護 全城罷工 不封不散<img 